
                     ####################################
                     Tinker Notes for LLVM flang on macOS
                     ####################################

         This subdirectory contains a set of script files that can be
         used to build the Tinker program package on a macOS system
         using LLVM clang/flang compilers under OpenMP parallelization.
         Some versions of clang do not enable building FFTW with OpenMP
         support. In those cases it is possible to link Tinker compiled
         under LLVM flang with FFTW libraries from GNU gcc.

